# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# CryoLab .gitignore — WHITELIST MODE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# PUBLIC REPO: bogie970/cryolab
# ONLY push: reference papers (PDFs) + status/journal for inter-agent comms
# EVERYTHING ELSE is prohibited from GitHub.
#
# LAW: Never commit secrets (tokens, webhooks, API keys, passwords).
# If accidentally committed, rotate immediately — it is BURNED.

# Block EVERYTHING by default
*
**/
**/*

# ── ALLOWED: This .gitignore ──
!.gitignore

# ── ALLOWED: Reference papers ──
!references/
!references/**
!references/NV_Physics/
!references/NV_Physics/**

# ── ALLOWED: Status/journal for inter-agent comms ──
!status/
!status/**

# ── Even within allowed dirs, block secrets ──
**/*.json
**/watchdog.json
**/*secret*
**/*credential*
**/*token*
**/.env
